column6: A 1x1 degree grid for the European Marine Waters
column11:
A 1x1 degree grid was created for the spatial extent of the European Register of Marine Species (ERMS). 
The marine area within the scope of the ERMS includes the continental shelf seas of Europe as well as the Mediterranean shelf, Baltic Seas and deep-sea areas (26??N -> 90??N and 45??W -> 70??E).
